<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><span class="title">Despite Exposure of Madoff Fraud, New Ponzi Schemes Emerge <span class="divider"> | </span></span> Financial regulators say a new Ponzi scheme operator is found nearly every week, and legal actions are brought against about 100 such questionable investment operations every year.<br /><span class="elsewhere"><a href="//dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/07/10/despite-exposure-of-madoff-fraud-new-ponzi-schemes-emerge/">DealBook &#187;</a></span></p>
